<http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://purl.org/dc/terms/title
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#resourceSensitivity
<http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#resourceSensitivity> rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


###  http://w3id.org/dpp/data-categories#espr-annex
:espr-annex rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty ;
            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> """References the ESPR Regulation Annex III section that
         mandates this data category in the DPP."""@en ;
            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "ESPR Annex reference"@en .


###  http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition
